            <h1 class="subtitle">6. Delivery of an Order</h1>
            <p>6.1. If the User orders the delivery of the Order through the Weydrop, the Order will be delivered to the location confirmed by the User in the Weydrop. The User also has to provide a street address for the confirmed location in the Weydrop. Delivery services are provided by the Partner to the User or Customer Organization. For Users located in Saudi Arabia in relation to food products purchased from certain Partners: Weydrop provides the delivery services to the User or Customer Organization.</p>
